		<h2 class="padding-bottom-20">Sign-Up</h2>
		<p>The answers provided by the users will generate a list of topics that will be used to curate personalized content. The users can choose to skip this process, and fill it out at a later time when prompted again.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="wrapper padding-bottom-60">
