	<div class="wrapper text-align-left padding-bottom-60">
		<h2 class="padding-bottom-20">Feed</h2>
		<p>From the generated topics, relevant content in the personalized feed section is curated. Users can add or remove topics, and set subscription settings for individual topics as well as the entire feed.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="wrapper padding-bottom-60">
		<img src="images/webmd/feed1.png" class="screen3 margin-right-30px">
