	<div class="wrapper text-align-left padding-bottom-60">
		<h2 class="padding-bottom-20">Tools</h2>
		<p>The tools on the existing app were given more intuitive names and icons, and were put into the tools section.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="wrapper padding-bottom-60">
		<div class="screen-float-left">
