	<div class="wrapper text-align-left padding-bottom-60">
		<h2 class="padding-bottom-20">Search</h2>
		<p>Different topic pages in the existing app were combined into one search section, and were given more intuitive icons. Users can either browse an A-Z list of each category, or use the categories as a search filter.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="wrapper padding-bottom-60">
		<img src="images/webmd/search.png" class="screen3 margin-right-30px">
		<img src="images/webmd/placeholder.png" class="screen3 margin-right-30px">
		<img src="images/webmd/placeholder.png" class="screen3">
	</div>
		<div class="wrapper text-align-left padding-bottom-60">
		<h2 class="padding-bottom-20">Connect</h2>
		<p>In addition to the existing feature of talking to your physician through WebMD, we also added a group share/messaging feature and combined them into the connect section. Users can instantly share content in their feed with their contacts, and receive tips from their doctors as well.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="wrapper">
		<img src="images/webmd/connect.png" class="screen3 margin-right-30px">
